  "message": "feat(demo): add demo mode to session detail page\n\nWhen navigating to /sessions/demo-xxx:\n- Detect demo sessions before lab mode check\n- Load demo data from fixtures\n- Render DemoSessionDetail with demo banner\n- Show session status, messages, and compiled artifact\n- Hide SessionActions and RefreshControls in demo mode\n- Show friendly error for invalid demo IDs\n\nWorks without lab mode enabled on public website.\n\nImplements brenner_bot-vn19\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
